\hline Parameter & I & .par \\
\hline Geometry/Doping & I & .tdr \\
\hline Lifetime & I & .tdr \\
\hline Save & 0 & _des.sav \\
\hline Load & I & _des.sav \\
\hline Device Plot (grid-based) & O & _des.tdr \\
